      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDSTAR HARMONY (2) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten second (20.06) in a P5 at this track last time out. Key player on best and worth another chance. SIR BAREFOOT (5) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fifth and beaten 3 lengths (20.47) at Capalaba. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Cannot be taken lightly. ATOMIC GHOST (3) was below latest but prior to that a Grade 6 winner in quick time (19.81) at this track in a Grade 6. Can improve sharply here. DON'T DAMN ME (1) comes off a (19.67) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 6 over 350m at Q Straight. Has already won out of this draw.",
